01:01:54.166 --> 01:01:56.706
which is safe to administer as a monotherapy.

1057
01:01:58.006 --> 01:02:01.766
When we cleave our linker, we get full dissociation of our mask

1058
01:02:02.286 --> 01:02:06.206
and return to activity of the non-masked active control, as shown in those dotted

