01:03:00.986 --> 01:03:03.666
control is more potent than migrolimab.

1075
01:03:04.086 --> 01:03:07.906
And actually, if you look on the right, when we mask this molecule, we actually

1076
01:03:08.026 --> 01:03:10.706
increase efficacy, driving several complete responses.

1077
01:03:11.906 --> 01:03:15.866
And we believe that the combination of both enhanced efficacy and

1078
01:03:15.906 --> 01:03:19.486
improved safety from the previous slide leads to a much superior

1079
01:03:19.496 --> 01:03:20.446
therapeutic index.

1080
01:03:23.066 --> 01:03:26.626
So, in conclusion, Vor101 is the first high-affinity

1081
01:03:26.666 --> 01:03:30.546
SIRPalpha CD47 binder fused with an

